  ('medical-tech-moex-05175', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-110-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關偏光顯微鏡之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["可以觀察具有雙折光性的物質", "載物台的設計常可以自由旋轉", "無法區別滑膜液尿酸鈉結晶（MSU）及焦磷酸鈣結晶（CPPD）", "使用一級紅色補色鏡（first-order red compensator），將光線分離成慢波及快波"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "50b45af8129b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f496f9a57809", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110020", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-05176', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-110-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於螢光顯微鏡之操作，以fluorescein isothiocyanate（FITC）螢光劑觀察時，下列何者正確？', '["使用495 nm激發光", "須選擇紫外激發濾鏡（ultraviolet excitation filter）以激發檢體", "不能使用浸油高倍率物鏡，因為油會產生影像色差缺陷（chromatic aberration）", "須選擇阻擋濾鏡（barrier filter），以收集檢體發出的495 nm螢光"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "50b45af8129b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f496f9a57809", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110020", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
